OL,3,CSnow and ice closes Isle of Man airport
OL,5,FNo flights will operate from the
OL,6,Fairport on the Isle of Man and all
OL,7,Fschools have been forced to close due
OL,8,Fto freezing temperatures and snow.
OL,10,FAn amber weather warning for ice and
OL,11,Fwintery showers is in place until noon
OL,12,Fon 5 January 2026, with temperatures
OL,13,Fexpected to rise above freezing
OL,14,Fovernight.
OL,16,FThe Isle of Man government confirmed
OL,17,Fthat the runway at Ronaldsway Airport
OL,18,Fremains "unsuitable for aircraft
OL,19,Foperations."
