OL,3,CSnow and ice closes Isle of Man airport
OL,5,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,6,F"Snow remains across the runway,
OL,7,Ftaxiways and apron, with icy
OL,8,Fconditions underneath.
OL,10,F"Temperatures are not expected to rise
OL,11,Fenough to allow effective melting,
OL,12,Fmeaning the runway remains unsuitable
OL,13,Ffor aircraft operations.
OL,15,F"While mechanical snow clearance has
OL,16,Ftaken place on parts of the apron,
OL,17,Fclearing the runway would create snow
OL,18,Fbanks that could lead to further
OL,19,Foperational issues.
