OL,3,CSnow and ice closes Isle of Man airport
OL,5,F"As a result, no flights will operate
OL,6,Ftoday. Terminal facilities are
OL,7,Flimited, and security is now closed to
OL,8,Fadditional passengers."
OL,10,FMeanwhile, all schools on the island
OL,11,Fand University College Isle of Man
OL,12,Fwill stay closed on Monday due to
OL,13,Fdangerous conditions and disruption to
OL,14,Fthe island's public transportation.
OL,16,FA spokesperson from the government
OL,17,Fsaid: "While some sites may be
OL,18,Faccessible, the safety of pupils and
OL,19,Fstaff remains the top priority."
