OL,3,CSnow and ice closes Isle of Man airport
OL,5,FThe facilities are expected to open as
OL,6,Fnormal on Tuesday, 6 January, as
OL,7,Ftemperatures warm up.
OL,9,FThe Mountain Road remains shut, with
OL,10,Fthe Department of Infrastructure
OL,11,Fsaying it will review this later on
OL,12,FMonday afternoon.
OL,14,FAll main roads remain open but people
OL,15,Fare urged to drive with caution, with
OL,16,Fresidents encouraged to allow extra
OL,17,Ftime for journeys.
