OL,3,CSnow and ice closes Isle of Man airport
OL,5,FMeanwhile, patients with appointments
OL,6,Fare both hospitals on the island are
OL,7,Fbeing encouraged to only travel "if it
OL,8,Fis safe to do so."
OL,10,FAnyone scheduled for essential renal
OL,11,For chemotherapy should still attend.
OL,12,FIf they cannot travel they should call
OL,13,Fhospital.
